Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz15.32\pos(620,533.333)}周二 升学就业会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz11.65\pos(662.667,939.333)}周四 运营委员会 提早下课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz16.33\pos(1316,181.333)}本月目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1305.333,397.333)\frz18.56}打招呼
