Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本月目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升学就业会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾经穿著校服 上著学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下节课是啥来著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想 语文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧把你的作业借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 又来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我爸妈吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们让我别练柔道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大赛怎办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[是那个家伙呀]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[好恶心哇]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多同龄人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又把这种东西带回学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会给没收的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别打小报告哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 就是那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啥时候就升级了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让我哥帮我打的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我能去你家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要让你去好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是他们干的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么老是只欺负我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,you 干掉他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么生气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干 掉 他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会轻松的多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快快发芽吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柿子的种子~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也已经烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了蜜柑会从那边拿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毘沙门…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毘沙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是毘沙耶 毘沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全副武装的今天有何指教吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这实在是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋 纴 绍 兆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是囷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是秋巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是纴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是绍巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是兆麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是我带的全部兵器了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今天上门拜访是为了听取凶兆占卜的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前从风穴跑出的妖怪已经基本清除干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里和……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有…我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囷巴先生 凶兆占卜是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绍是新人所以不清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐偶尔会来问小福大神风穴打开的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}该选哪一个才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她指示的地方几乎一说一个准
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是小福大人的指示 说是时化也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纴巴小姐这话可…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴会在意想不到的地方打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其事后弥补 不如事前做好准备 灾祸也能降到最少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺多的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毘沙好辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱除妖怪得再加油了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 小福殿下和夜卜好像是熟人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是为了让我远离夜卜 故意打开风穴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我家神也不会做这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我和夜卜的因缘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这和我无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是小夜卜出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就做好觉悟…会有大时化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然可以吓退那个毘沙门欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越来越崇拜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 我的心里不知为何好焦躁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还不放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这件事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时小夜卜感染恙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还在学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天没闻到夜卜的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他看起来很累
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果丢著不管的话痛苦会累积
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恙会遍布全身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想确确…确认一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙正处于难搞的年龄段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音永远停在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现时化了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪个小鬼引起的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这样觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞笑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到那时候那家伙的表情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就觉得闻到一股垃圾臭味原来是学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么 有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那副嘴脸算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,you 干掉他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 那就是个玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛当真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩笑?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相应的代价是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要让对手握有相同的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坑我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一线 跨过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越 一线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越 一线的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会舒服了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨过去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨过去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨过去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乐园就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越一线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变轻松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不想再做人了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真会悬崖勒马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想要是情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就往那上面泼点净化的水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起了...夜卜先生说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用这种东西伤了人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会真的无处容身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃做人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在这里坚持住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来又会被大家无视了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 现在的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得人多的一方就会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去寻找那个对你来说独一无二的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点就变成危险的事态了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方都吓得尿裤子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会对别人说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能找到个好朋友就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的话没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独一...无二的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某人...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也带我走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来...终于察觉到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才不能去彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有你想要的那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起钱 真正想要的东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无法得到了 你知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这一道界线...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么 都不能跨越啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么 刚才的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 快退后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是被恙污染了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜 振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去找那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是恙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直在承受 这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜一直在忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音每做一次坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜就会有这样痛苦的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 夜卜还是一直承受著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但...但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我也能好好阻止雪音就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小福 晚饭前别吃太多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天客人出奇得多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,境界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快打开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大黑先生 小福小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜...夜卜要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东风若吹起...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道真公 差不多该吟诵新的和歌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅雨真会强人所难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 野良神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.21,0:24:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 道真公
